    "score" : 13,
    "last_activity_date" : 1383027114,
    "last_edit_date" : 1383027114,
    "creation_date" : 1383026976,
    "answer_id" : 19650948,
    "question_id" : 19650917,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Use <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/math/BigDecimal.html#doubleValue%28%29\" rel=\"noreferrer\">doubleValue</a> method present in <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/math/BigDecimal.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">BigDecimal</a> class :</p>\n\n<pre><code>double doubleValue()\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Converts this <code>BigDecimal</code> to a <code>double</code>.</p>\n"
  }, {
