    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can convert <code>BigDecimal</code> to <code>double</code> using <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/math/BigDecimal.html#doubleValue%28%29\"><code>.doubleValue()</code></a>. But believe me, don't use it if you have currency manipulations. It should always be performed on <code>BigDecimal</code> objects directly. Precision loss in these calculations are big time problems in currency related calculations.</p>\n"
