  "body" : "<p>How we convert <code>BigDecimal</code> into <code>Double</code> in java? I have a requirement where we have to use Double as argument but we are getting <code>BigDecimal</code> so i have to convert <code>BigDecimal</code> into <code>Double</code>.</p>\n"
